# Workflow B: Multi-Stage Pipeline

**Must** follow skill `@rtl-pipeline-workflow-b`; read `SKILL.en.md`.

## Paths

| Artifact | Path |
|----------|------|
| Original SPEC (read-only) | `spec/` |
| Refined SPEC | `workflow-b-pipeline/spec_refined.md` |
| Timing plan | `workflow-b-pipeline/timing_plan.md` |
| Collaboration log | `workflow-b-pipeline/collaboration_log.md` |
| RTL | `workflow-b-pipeline/rtl/*.v` |

## Forbidden

- Editing originals under `spec/`
- Agent3 generating RTL from raw `spec/` only
- Mixing Workflow A and B RTL directories

## Read scope (Pass@1 fairness)

| Agent | Allowed reads |
|-------|----------------|
| Agent1 | `spec/` |
| Agent2 | `spec/`, `spec_refined.md`, `collaboration_log.md` |
| Agent3 | `spec_refined.md`, `timing_plan.md`, `collaboration_log.md` |

**All agents must not** read `RTLLM/`, `verified_*.v`, `testbench.v`, `_chatgpt35/`, `_chatgpt4/`. Record `[ASSUMPTION]` or stop; do not fill gaps from reference RTL.

## Sub-tasks

- Agent1 / refine SPEC → `spec_refined.md`
- Agent2 / timing plan → `timing_plan.md` + log
- Agent3 / RTL → `workflow-b-pipeline/rtl/`
- Full pipeline → Agent1 → Agent2 (collaboration) → Agent3
